### PCF Next-Gen — AR / VR ultra-low latency examples
### Base URL (local): http://localhost:9080

@base = http://localhost:9080

### 1) Pre-seeded demo subscriber (GET)
GET {{base}}/demo/ar-vr/policy
Accept: application/json

### 2) Intent-based policy — stadium AR (POST)
POST {{base}}/npcf-sba/v1/policy/intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "intent": {
    "intent_id": "ULTRA_LOW_LATENCY_AR",
    "description": "Immersive AR for venue slice",
    "target_latency_ms_p99": 12,
    "min_downlink_mbps": 80,
    "slice_hint": "stadium-urllc",
    "application_id": "com.example.ar.stadium"
  },
  "session": {
    "subscriber_id": "ar-demo-001",
    "imsi": "001010987654321",
    "network_generation": "5G",
    "apn": "ims.enterprise-ar",
    "service_type": "web_browsing",
    "application_id": "com.example.ar.stadium",
    "location": "stadium-42"
  }
}

### 3) SBA-style flat policy decision (POST)
POST {{base}}/npcf-sba/v1/policy/decision
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriber_id": "ar-demo-001",
  "imsi": "001010987654321",
  "network_generation": "5G",
  "apn": "ims.enterprise-ar",
  "service_type": "low_latency",
  "application_id": "com.example.ar.stadium",
  "location": "stadium-42"
}

### 4) Closed-loop telemetry → adjustment suggestion
POST {{base}}/npcf-sba/v1/closed-loop/telemetry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cell_id": "nr-cell-stadium-01",
  "congestion_score": 0.91,
  "mean_user_throughput_mbps": 42,
  "mean_latency_ms": 55,
  "active_ues": 812
}

### 5) Monetization quote (CHF-ready keys)
POST {{base}}/nchf-ready/v1/quote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_class": "ar",
  "requested_downlink_mbps": 100,
  "expected_latency_ms_p99": 12,
  "duration_seconds": 3600,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### 6) Digital twin simulation (shadow decision)
POST {{base}}/npcf-sba/v1/simulation/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriber_id": "ar-demo-001",
  "imsi": "001010987654321",
  "network_generation": "5G",
  "apn": "ims.enterprise-ar",
  "service_type": "low_latency",
  "application_id": "com.example.ar.stadium"
}
